[quote=“BloodyRage, post:2, topic:76529”]In Client.java
search for

case 315: //Shrimps

And it should say somewhere near it…

healing[1] = 3;healing[2] = 3;

change the "3"s to what you want it to heal… and search for sharks/manta rays or any food you want to change. :)[/quote]
